videos.headline: Bonnafon extends Cardinals lead
videos.description: Reggie Bonnafon runs 64 yards to the end zone for a Louisville touchdown.

videos.headline: Big play by Brown for the Eagles' 1st down
videos.description: Boston College QB Anthony Brown runs 30 yards to the Louisville 18 -yard line.

videos.headline: Dillon scores for Eagles'
videos.description: AJ Dillon runs 1 yard for a Boston College touchdown.

videos.headline: BC cashes in with 42-yard TD
videos.description: Boston College's Anthony Brown  finds Thadd Smith wide open for a 42-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Dillon's 2nd TD ties game
videos.description: AJ Dillon's runs it from  3 yards to make the score 21-21.

videos.headline: Hilliman's TD puts BC in front
videos.description: Jon Hilliman's 6-yard touchdown run puts the Eagles' ahead in the the third quarter.

videos.headline: Jackson throws INT to set up BC
videos.description: Boston College's Wyatt Ray picks off Lamar Jackson's pass.

videos.headline: Jackson connects with Averett for TD on 4th down
videos.description: Lamar Jackson finds Kemari Averett along the sidelines, who dives into the end zone for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Jackson uses option to weave into the end zone
videos.description: Lamar Jackson fakes the handoff and runs 20 yards for a Louisville touchdown.

videos.headline: Dillon's 3rd TD extends Eagles' lead
videos.description: AJ Dillon rushes 11 yards to the end zone to increase Boston College's lead to 35-21.

videos.headline: Jackson finds Fitzpatrick for TD
videos.description: Lamar Jackson delivers a 40-yard touchdown pass to Dez Fitzpatrick.

videos.headline: Dillon's 75-yard touchdown run
videos.description: AJ Dillon rushes down the sidelines for 75-yards for his fourth touchdown of the game.

videos.headline: Jackson breezes to the end zone
videos.description: Lamar Jackson runs 9 yards for a Cardinals touchdown.

videos.headline: Louisville turnover gives Boston College another chance
videos.description: Cardinals' Jaylen Smith loses the football and Kamrin Moore recovers to give the Eagles' good field position.

videos.headline: FG wins it for Eagles'
videos.description: Colton Litchenberg hits the 27-yard field goal to give Boston College 45-42 win over Louisville.
